1
00:00:04,360 --> 00:00:05,420
Take them all away!

2
00:00:05,600 --> 00:00:06,330
Arrest them!

3
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:09,590
Stop!

4
00:00:09,830 --> 00:00:11,030
What are you doing?

5
00:00:11,030 --> 00:00:12,360
This place is suspected of
spreading rumors,

6
00:00:12,360 --> 00:00:14,070
inciting disturbances,
and manipulating people's minds.

7
00:00:14,070 --> 00:00:14,930
Take them away!

8
00:00:15,270 --> 00:00:15,590
Move!

9
00:00:15,590 --> 00:00:16,190
Slander!

10
00:00:16,510 --> 00:00:17,410
This is pure slander!

11
00:00:17,410 --> 00:00:18,120
Let me go!

12
00:00:18,710 --> 00:00:19,520
-Move!
-This is just wicked!

13
00:00:19,520 --> 00:00:20,250
Move faster!

14
00:00:20,340 --> 00:00:21,650
This is pure slander!

15
00:00:26,960 --> 00:00:28,090
Quick, come with me.

16
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:28,710
After him!

17
00:00:28,710 --> 00:00:29,410
[Episode 11: Unyielding Through
Countless Trials and Hardships]

18
00:00:29,410 --> 00:00:30,610
Don't let him escape!

19
00:01:07,560 --> 00:01:10,810
[Luminosity Behind The Palace]

20
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,740
We're here, hurry.

21
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:18,680
Sir, come on in.

22
00:01:21,400 --> 00:01:21,920
Sir.

23
00:01:22,200 --> 00:01:22,680
Sir.

24
00:01:23,310 --> 00:01:24,110
We meet again.

25
00:01:26,560 --> 00:01:27,430
May I ask

26
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:29,590
who you two really are?

27
00:01:30,560 --> 00:01:31,680
I am Su Leyu.

28
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:35,060
Your Highness, Consort Xian?

29
00:01:36,120 --> 00:01:36,920
And you are...

30
00:01:37,370 --> 00:01:38,170
Your Majesty?

31
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,860
Greetings, Your Majesty.

32
00:01:41,070 --> 00:01:42,729
No need for formalities, Sir.

33
00:01:45,009 --> 00:01:47,350
Your Majesty and Your Highness
have saved me today.

34
00:01:47,350 --> 00:01:48,009
I wonder...

35
00:01:48,710 --> 00:01:49,280
Mr. Lu.

36
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,130
You should have seen

37
00:01:51,390 --> 00:01:53,789
what your constant forbearance has led to.

38
00:01:54,039 --> 00:01:55,509
Your daughter died
after passing the imperial examination,

39
00:01:55,509 --> 00:01:57,120
and your academy was destroyed.

40
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:57,960
Mr. Lu,

41
00:01:58,350 --> 00:01:59,200
blind forbearance

42
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:01,870
cannot truly protect the scholars
in this world.

43
00:02:01,870 --> 00:02:03,130
The more you tolerate,

44
00:02:03,220 --> 00:02:05,150
the more they will take advantage.

45
00:02:07,950 --> 00:02:08,870
I am to blame

46
00:02:09,280 --> 00:02:10,520
for my incompetence.

47
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:12,690
When you asked me before

48
00:02:13,010 --> 00:02:15,070
if I had seen that poetry collection,

49
00:02:15,550 --> 00:02:17,520
I didn't want to cause more trouble,

50
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:19,190
so I didn't tell you the truth.

51
00:02:20,010 --> 00:02:21,340
That poetry collection

52
00:02:21,840 --> 00:02:24,300
failed to eliminate the corrupt officials,

53
00:02:24,340 --> 00:02:26,470
but cost my daughter her life instead.

54
00:02:30,150 --> 00:02:31,750
Sir, was your dismissal from office

55
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:33,079
related to this matter?

56
00:02:35,630 --> 00:02:37,030
I discovered that in the guest lists of

57
00:02:37,030 --> 00:02:38,590
major noble families'
birthday celebrations,

58
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:40,840
there were many students who had just
taken the imperial examination.

59
00:02:40,840 --> 00:02:41,630
I suspected

60
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:43,680
those students attending the banquets

61
00:02:43,680 --> 00:02:46,280
were seeking patronage from noble families
for recommendations.

62
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:46,760
So

63
00:02:47,079 --> 00:02:48,640
I proposed to the late empress

64
00:02:48,640 --> 00:02:50,280
to reform the imperial examination system.

65
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:50,350
[In the 21st Year of Jianing]

66
00:02:50,350 --> 00:02:51,150
Your Majesty,

67
00:02:51,470 --> 00:02:52,800
with the imperial examination approaching,

68
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,150
many scholars have entered the capital,

69
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,130
paying visits everywhere

70
00:02:55,130 --> 00:02:56,190
seeking recommendations.

71
00:02:56,190 --> 00:02:56,400
[Lu Jiuzhang, Right Vice Director
of the Department of State Affairs]

72
00:02:56,400 --> 00:02:56,930
However,

73
00:02:57,050 --> 00:02:57,960
these recommendations

74
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,450
are extremely unfair to other candidates.

75
00:02:59,450 --> 00:03:00,120
[Wang Zhan, Deputy Minister of Justice;
Qin Qiu, Premier]

76
00:03:00,120 --> 00:03:00,840
I propose

77
00:03:01,130 --> 00:03:03,190
abolishing the system of
noble family recommendations

78
00:03:03,190 --> 00:03:03,780
to ensure

79
00:03:03,990 --> 00:03:06,070
fairness in the imperial examination.

80
00:03:06,070 --> 00:03:06,830
Approved.

81
00:03:07,470 --> 00:03:08,870
Thank you, Your Majesty.

82
00:03:09,570 --> 00:03:10,520
Little did I know

83
00:03:10,830 --> 00:03:12,770
that this action would bring me
utter ruin.

84
00:03:12,770 --> 00:03:13,280
[Lu Residence]

85
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:15,120
They used the pretext of subversive poetry

86
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,310
to arrest me.

87
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:17,240
Prime Minister Lu.

88
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,120
You left this subversive poetry

89
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:19,400
deliberately in the palace.

90
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,910
How dare you slander Her Majesty!

91
00:03:20,910 --> 00:03:21,430
Take him away!

92
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:23,070
This is slander!
I demand to see Her Majesty!

93
00:03:23,070 --> 00:03:24,600
I demand to see Her Majesty!

94
00:03:27,000 --> 00:03:27,840
That poem

95
00:03:28,310 --> 00:03:29,870
was indeed written by me.

96
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:33,590
The noble families' spies and informants
are all over the court and the country.

97
00:03:33,590 --> 00:03:35,150
My intention was to use poetry

98
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:37,079
to remind the late empress
to take precautions early.

99
00:03:37,079 --> 00:03:38,140
I never expected it

100
00:03:38,260 --> 00:03:39,800
to be intercepted by those
from the noble families

101
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:41,110
and falsely accused as subversive writing.

102
00:03:41,110 --> 00:03:43,470
At that time,
we happened to be facing foreign invasion,

103
00:03:43,470 --> 00:03:46,590
and the late empress needed their power
to resist the enemy.

104
00:03:46,590 --> 00:03:48,160
She had no choice but to
consider the bigger picture,

105
00:03:48,160 --> 00:03:49,150
so she dismissed me from office

106
00:03:49,150 --> 00:03:50,680
in order to protect my life.

107
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:52,560
From that moment on,

108
00:03:53,090 --> 00:03:54,710
I became increasingly concerned

109
00:03:54,710 --> 00:03:56,840
about Dacang's political situation.

110
00:03:57,710 --> 00:03:58,740
After that,

111
00:03:59,150 --> 00:04:02,090
I took my family and retreated
to live in seclusion in the mountains.

112
00:04:02,090 --> 00:04:05,100
I taught Yueying from a young age
about etiquette, integrity,

113
00:04:05,100 --> 00:04:06,900
and the principles of
being a righteous person.

114
00:04:06,900 --> 00:04:09,410
Yueying also befriended many scholars
from humble families

115
00:04:09,410 --> 00:04:11,210
and people with great ambition.

116
00:04:11,450 --> 00:04:12,490
In them,

117
00:04:13,010 --> 00:04:14,890
I saw hope for Dacang once again.

118
00:04:15,550 --> 00:04:17,410
But the noble families were
really powerful,

119
00:04:17,410 --> 00:04:19,269
and I worried that if discovered,

120
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:21,690
it would affect
the future of those scholars.

121
00:04:21,690 --> 00:04:22,450
So,

122
00:04:23,240 --> 00:04:25,700
I used the legend of
the fox demon as a pretext

123
00:04:25,730 --> 00:04:27,430
to only teach at night.

124
00:04:30,270 --> 00:04:31,030
Mr. Lu.

125
00:04:35,390 --> 00:04:36,720
Later, Yueying discovered

126
00:04:36,720 --> 00:04:38,950
the evidence I had hidden
in my poetry collection.

127
00:04:38,950 --> 00:04:41,550
She learned I had been framed
by noble families

128
00:04:41,790 --> 00:04:44,159
and decided to clear my name.

129
00:04:44,850 --> 00:04:47,580
I knew this was like
throwing eggs against a rock,

130
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,800
so I removed the evidence

131
00:04:49,820 --> 00:04:51,310
from the poetry collection.

132
00:04:51,310 --> 00:04:51,800
Father.

133
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:55,580
You went to the Imperial Academy?

134
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,310
If you're taking the imperial examination

135
00:04:57,310 --> 00:04:58,810
merely for fame and fortune,

136
00:04:58,810 --> 00:04:59,940
that's your choice.

137
00:05:00,840 --> 00:05:02,120
But if it's for anything else,

138
00:05:02,120 --> 00:05:03,450
I absolutely forbid it!

139
00:05:05,190 --> 00:05:05,680
Father,

140
00:05:08,180 --> 00:05:10,920
the future of scholars
from humble families across the land

141
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:13,190
is about to be destroyed
by this corrupt officialdom,

142
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:14,310
as you well know!

143
00:05:14,950 --> 00:05:15,950
The sages once said,

144
00:05:15,950 --> 00:05:19,210
"When the Great Way is followed,
the world belongs to all."

145
00:05:19,390 --> 00:05:21,280
The sages traveled through various states

146
00:05:21,280 --> 00:05:23,940
only to advise rulers
to practice benevolent governance.

147
00:05:23,940 --> 00:05:24,540
Today,

148
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:27,460
I too wish to follow their example

149
00:05:29,140 --> 00:05:31,100
and establish myself with integrity.

150
00:05:31,100 --> 00:05:31,540
You...

151
00:05:38,430 --> 00:05:38,890
Father.

152
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:40,270
Father!

153
00:05:43,080 --> 00:05:44,270
I failed to stop her.

154
00:05:47,890 --> 00:05:49,420
It's my fault that she died.

155
00:05:53,680 --> 00:05:54,480
Your Majesty,

156
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:56,790
please forgive my incompetence.

157
00:05:56,790 --> 00:05:58,740
I couldn't even protect my own daughter.

158
00:05:58,740 --> 00:06:01,090
How could I possibly protect
scholars across the land?

159
00:06:01,090 --> 00:06:02,690
Regarding Yueying's death,

160
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:05,060
it's better not to investigate further.

161
00:06:06,030 --> 00:06:08,440
Don't you want to seek justice
for your daughter?

162
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:10,700
Lu Yueying, full of talent and ambition,

163
00:06:11,120 --> 00:06:12,580
only to be falsely accused

164
00:06:12,750 --> 00:06:14,350
of cheating after her death.

165
00:06:14,750 --> 00:06:16,040
Of course I want to!

166
00:06:16,930 --> 00:06:18,660
But if I tried to clear her name,

167
00:06:18,690 --> 00:06:20,510
those passionate scholars

168
00:06:20,530 --> 00:06:21,990
would surely follow suit.

169
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:23,910
If they were to face retaliation
from noble families because of this,

170
00:06:23,910 --> 00:06:25,620
I would be harming them.

171
00:06:29,440 --> 00:06:32,570
I am well aware that
the court has been corrupt for years,

172
00:06:32,680 --> 00:06:34,060
with noble families controlling
the imperial examinations

173
00:06:34,060 --> 00:06:35,750
and blocking talented people's paths.

174
00:06:35,750 --> 00:06:36,950
I have always desired

175
00:06:37,190 --> 00:06:38,790
to break this corrupt system

176
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:41,650
and to establish
a fairer selection process,

177
00:06:42,300 --> 00:06:43,640
allowing talented individuals

178
00:06:43,640 --> 00:06:44,840
to serve the court

179
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:46,420
regardless of gender.

180
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:58,000
Mr. Lu.

181
00:06:59,720 --> 00:07:01,850
This was also the late empress's wish.

182
00:07:04,500 --> 00:07:06,960
The imperial examination
was never easy for women.

183
00:07:06,960 --> 00:07:08,320
Lu Yueying had great aspirations,

184
00:07:08,320 --> 00:07:09,520
exceptional talent,

185
00:07:09,890 --> 00:07:12,020
and could have had a brilliant future.

186
00:07:12,210 --> 00:07:14,170
Yet she risked offending noble families

187
00:07:14,170 --> 00:07:16,570
to fight for a fair chance
for all scholars.

188
00:07:17,100 --> 00:07:20,300
Are you willing to hide like this
for the rest of your life?

189
00:07:20,580 --> 00:07:22,980
You are the father
Lu Yueying admired most,

190
00:07:23,410 --> 00:07:25,070
yet you've been trying to protect yourself
and avoid trouble,

191
00:07:25,070 --> 00:07:27,270
neither fighting for
a fairer examination system

192
00:07:27,270 --> 00:07:30,190
nor defending your daughter
against false accusations.

193
00:07:30,190 --> 00:07:30,870
Mr. Lu.

194
00:07:31,880 --> 00:07:34,409
When you meet your daughter
in the afterlife,

195
00:07:36,190 --> 00:07:37,870
how will you face her?

196
00:07:55,520 --> 00:07:57,380
I've spent half my life drifting,

197
00:07:58,040 --> 00:07:59,830
like a dull knife being worn down,

198
00:07:59,830 --> 00:08:02,430
not realizing I had become
so numb and decayed.

199
00:08:03,190 --> 00:08:04,510
Your words today, Your Highness,

200
00:08:04,510 --> 00:08:05,920
have awakened me.

201
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:09,630
Very well.

202
00:08:11,710 --> 00:08:12,750
Today, I'll

203
00:08:13,050 --> 00:08:14,120
join Your Majesty

204
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:15,940
and Your Highness,

205
00:08:16,480 --> 00:08:18,000
join all scholars,

206
00:08:18,210 --> 00:08:19,980
and join Yueying

207
00:08:21,070 --> 00:08:22,110
to clear the skies

208
00:08:22,650 --> 00:08:24,120
and cleanse the world!

209
00:08:34,150 --> 00:08:35,000
I hid the list

210
00:08:35,440 --> 00:08:36,900
sewn inside this garment.

211
00:08:37,080 --> 00:08:39,320
Just compare it with those
who passed the examination that year,

212
00:08:39,320 --> 00:08:41,049
and you'll discover the truth.

213
00:08:43,390 --> 00:08:44,270
Thank you, Sir.

214
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:48,940
You stay here with Mr. Lu.

215
00:08:48,950 --> 00:08:50,010
I'll be right back.

216
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:51,370
Leyu,

217
00:08:51,770 --> 00:08:53,230
you must be extra careful.

218
00:08:53,400 --> 00:08:54,140
You too.

219
00:08:57,260 --> 00:08:59,070
[Ningzheng Hall]

220
00:08:59,910 --> 00:09:00,710
Your Majesty.

221
00:09:01,090 --> 00:09:02,220
I have verified that

222
00:09:02,460 --> 00:09:03,970
those on the birthday banquet list

223
00:09:03,970 --> 00:09:06,550
are indeed all those who passed
the imperial examination that year.

224
00:09:06,550 --> 00:09:07,000
Now,

225
00:09:07,310 --> 00:09:08,320
they've all been appointed as officials

226
00:09:08,320 --> 00:09:10,040
in various regional prefectures

227
00:09:10,040 --> 00:09:11,770
or as key personnel in Zhongdu.

228
00:09:20,860 --> 00:09:22,320
I just compared the lists,

229
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:24,450
and this Wang Lin seems very suspicious.

230
00:09:24,450 --> 00:09:26,350
Go investigate the Hanlin Academy scholar,
Wang Lin,

231
00:09:26,350 --> 00:09:27,750
to see if he ever held

232
00:09:27,770 --> 00:09:29,360
similar banquets
before or after the imperial examination.

233
00:09:29,360 --> 00:09:29,870
If so,

234
00:09:29,930 --> 00:09:31,440
be sure to verify it thoroughly.

235
00:09:31,440 --> 00:09:33,100
As you command, Your Majesty.

236
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,310
Your Majesty,

237
00:09:37,310 --> 00:09:38,590
as you ordered,

238
00:09:38,990 --> 00:09:40,790
we've arranged secret protection
for the academy

239
00:09:40,790 --> 00:09:42,030
and Mr. Lu.

240
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,790
Recently, Wang Lin

241
00:09:47,790 --> 00:09:49,360
held a grand birthday celebration
for his mother.

242
00:09:49,360 --> 00:09:50,820
The people on the gift list

243
00:09:51,150 --> 00:09:52,920
were all
on the second-rank candidate list.

244
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:53,730
Wang Lin?

245
00:09:55,150 --> 00:09:57,360
So the person Liu Wenchong saw that night

246
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:58,840
who was arguing with Lu Yueying

247
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,920
could be Wang Lin.

248
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:04,080
Because Wang Lin
can be addressed as a scholar.

249
00:10:04,150 --> 00:10:04,840
And

250
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:06,400
in the darkness of night,

251
00:10:06,960 --> 00:10:09,160
Liu Wenchong might have been mistaken.

252
00:10:10,870 --> 00:10:12,730
They are now using the same method

253
00:10:13,160 --> 00:10:14,760
to bribe the examiners.

254
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,510
As long as they don't tamper with
the top three candidates,

255
00:10:17,510 --> 00:10:19,470
it won't attract too much attention.

256
00:10:19,470 --> 00:10:21,440
Wang Lin must have wanted
to win Lu Yueying over,

257
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,840
which is why they argued.

258
00:10:24,150 --> 00:10:25,840
Having secured the top three,

259
00:10:26,610 --> 00:10:29,010
they'd then assign those
who passed the imperial examination

260
00:10:29,010 --> 00:10:30,550
to various important positions

261
00:10:30,550 --> 00:10:32,600
through noble family recommendations.

262
00:10:32,600 --> 00:10:33,260
In this way,

263
00:10:33,470 --> 00:10:36,200
Dacang would be
completely under their control.

264
00:10:37,550 --> 00:10:38,350
Your Majesty,

265
00:10:38,400 --> 00:10:39,730
we must act decisively,

266
00:10:39,730 --> 00:10:41,930
or it may drag on and cause more trouble.

267
00:10:43,150 --> 00:10:44,930
Speaking of how to investigate Wang Lin,

268
00:10:44,930 --> 00:10:45,560
it seems

269
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:48,120
the Justice Bureau must step in.

270
00:10:48,890 --> 00:10:52,080
How about I disguise myself
as an officer from the Justice Bureau

271
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:53,190
and join the operation?

272
00:10:53,190 --> 00:10:54,190
What do you think?

273
00:10:56,010 --> 00:10:57,740
Then be sure to be very careful.

274
00:11:07,490 --> 00:11:08,550
You must be hungry.

275
00:11:09,250 --> 00:11:11,740
I've brought some food
specially for Your Majesty.

276
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:13,470
Your Majesty has a sweet tooth.

277
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:14,440
Try this.

278
00:11:18,130 --> 00:11:20,350
♪ A thousand words to say ♪

279
00:11:20,830 --> 00:11:22,320
♪ Yet I know not how to speak them ♪

280
00:11:22,320 --> 00:11:23,440
Only you know

