00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:57,520
First, detain everyone in the residence.

329
00:13:57,520 --> 00:13:58,390
You must be quick.

330
00:13:58,390 --> 00:13:58,910
Got it!

331
00:14:04,630 --> 00:14:06,430
