334
00:14:10,270 --> 00:14:12,150
You aren't really a traitor,

335
00:14:12,850 --> 00:14:15,050
so why would there be any talk of spying?

336
00:14:15,670 --> 00:14:16,440
Yin Cong.

337
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:19,440
The hidden tumor will soon be exposed.

338
00:14:20,310 --> 00:14:22,510
