Lord Yin!

343
00:15:17,870 --> 00:15:18,910
What's this supposed to mean?

344
00:15:18,910 --> 00:15:19,670
Lord Wang.

345
00:15:20,170 --> 00:15:21,170
Don't be nervous.

346
00:15:22,790 --> 00:15:23,480
Let me go!

347
00:15:24,200 --> 00:15:24,800
Let me go!

348
00:15:25,440 --> 00:15:25,970
Lord Yin!

349
00:15:26,160 --> 00:15:27,760
