350
00:15:27,910 --> 00:15:28,570
Lord Yin!

351
00:15:36,960 --> 00:15:37,670
Lord Wang.

352
00:15:38,150 --> 00:15:41,280
You truly have remarkable achievements
in governance.

353
00:15:43,290 --> 00:15:44,820
You'll have to come with me.

354
00:15:52,790 --> 00:15:53,590
Your Majesty.

355
00:15:55,060 --> 00:15:57,110
The Justice Bureau has investigated
Wang Lin's household

356
00:15:57,110 --> 00:16:00,040
and found a great deal of illegal wealth
as expected.

357
00:16:01,550 --> 00:16:03,210
The members of the Wang family

358
00:16:03,300 --> 00:16:05,100
must be eradicated completely.

359
00:16:06,900 --> 00:16:09,310
[Justice Bureau]

360
00:16:21,950 --> 00:16:23,500
The 29th year of Jianing...

361
00:16:43,930 --> 00:16:45,860
September 6, 29th year of Jianing.

362
00:16:49,940 --> 00:16:50,910
My guess was right.

363
00:16:50,910 --> 00:16:52,860
That night, a group of officers
from the Justice Bureau

364
00:16:52,860 --> 00:16:54,320
did go to Xuanji Pavilion.

365
00:16:54,860 --> 00:16:55,750
There's no record here

366
00:16:55,750 --> 00:16:57,200
of them reporting back,

367
00:16:58,550 --> 00:16:59,410
which means...

368
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:03,650
Which means they never returned.

369
00:17:40,330 --> 00:17:41,930
The Justice Bureau Duty Log.

370
00:17:43,850 --> 00:17:45,910
Leyu, you've been investigating me.

371
00:17:51,480 --> 00:17:54,080
So you're indeed spying on me
for Yin Changyan.

372
00:17:54,350 --> 00:17:55,380
Director Yin.

373
00:17:57,480 --> 00:17:58,690
How does it feel

374
00:17:59,000 --> 00:17:59,920
to be betrayed?

375
00:18:00,940 --> 00:18:04,000
What brings you here so late at night,
Grand Preceptor?

376
00:18:04,200 --> 00:18:06,330
I've come to ask for a favor, of course.

377
00:18:07,490 --> 00:18:10,220
The mighty Grand Preceptor,
with all your power,

378
00:18:10,800 --> 00:18:13,330
coming to ask a mere Director
like me for help?

379
00:18:14,320 --> 00:18:15,990
Su Leyu and Yin Changyan

380
00:18:16,020 --> 00:18:17,550
have so little faith in you.

381
00:18:17,750 --> 00:18:19,950
Don't you want to do something about it?

382
00:18:20,590 --> 00:18:22,920
What do you want me to do,
Grand Preceptor?

383
00:18:23,340 --> 00:18:26,140
Show your loyalty to
His Majesty and Consort Xian,

384
00:18:26,580 --> 00:18:28,970
then we can plan our next move.

385
00:18:29,700 --> 00:18:30,780
What makes you think

386
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:32,210
I would take your side?

387
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:38,600
The Xi family is gone,

388
00:18:39,800 --> 00:18:41,860
and the Wang family will soon follow.

389
00:18:42,110 --> 00:18:43,680
The Qin family will be next.

390
00:18:45,050 --> 00:18:46,180
You will agree,

391
00:18:47,140 --> 00:18:48,170
Qin Cong.

392
00:19:04,310 --> 00:19:05,710
Go find something for me.

393
00:19:06,070 --> 00:19:06,670
What is it?

394
00:19:07,800 --> 00:19:10,990
It grows in extremely damp,
shaded places in the mountains.

395
00:19:10,990 --> 00:19:12,050
Search carefully.

396
00:19:13,120 --> 00:19:13,640
Yes.

397
00:19:18,780 --> 00:19:23,010
[Imperial Academy]

398
00:19:23,040 --> 00:19:24,970
News just came from the palace that

399
00:19:25,030 --> 00:19:27,320
the investigation into
the examination fraud case is complete.

400
00:19:27,320 --> 00:19:29,580
Hanlin Academy scholar Wang Lin
has been dismissed,

401
00:19:29,580 --> 00:19:30,890
and his family's property
has been confiscated.

402
00:19:30,890 --> 00:19:31,620
In one month,

403
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:32,830
the imperial examination
will be held again.

404
00:19:32,830 --> 00:19:33,550
What?

405
00:19:33,900 --> 00:19:35,970
The imperial examination
will be held again?

406
00:19:35,970 --> 00:19:37,960
Although Wang Lin has been dismissed,

407
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:38,900
the noble families

408
00:19:38,900 --> 00:19:40,230
still hold great power.

409
00:19:40,510 --> 00:19:41,890
If this matter isn't
thoroughly investigated,

410
00:19:41,890 --> 00:19:43,350
how can we put an end to the cheating?

411
00:19:43,350 --> 00:19:44,070
That's right!

412
00:19:44,070 --> 00:19:44,600
Exactly!

413
00:19:45,190 --> 00:19:45,990
Not only that,

414
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:47,800
if the current imperial examination system
isn't reformed,

415
00:19:47,800 --> 00:19:50,310
the poison of corruption
will surely return.

416
00:19:50,310 --> 00:19:50,910
Everyone,

417
00:19:51,350 --> 00:19:52,940
I am willing to represent us all

418
00:19:52,940 --> 00:19:54,060
to beat the drum of grievance

419
00:19:54,060 --> 00:19:55,260
and petition His Majesty!

420
00:19:55,260 --> 00:19:55,700
Right!

421
00:19:55,720 --> 00:19:56,880
Let's petition His Majesty!

422
00:19:56,880 --> 00:20:01,190
Petition His Majesty!
Petition His Majesty!

423
00:20:02,350 --> 00:20:04,160
[Justice Bureau]

424
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:09,960
Leyu, where are you going
dressed like this?

425
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:11,240
There are patrol officers on the streets.

426
00:20:11,240 --> 00:20:12,640
What if you get spotted?

427
00:20:14,440 --> 00:20:15,770
Why do you care about me?

428
00:20:16,290 --> 00:20:18,000
Aren't you afraid I'd spy on you

429
00:20:18,000 --> 00:20:19,460
for that usurper anymore?

430
00:20:22,350 --> 00:20:22,920
Leyu.

431
00:20:23,900 --> 00:20:26,160
I admit that whenever I think of
what happened at Xuanji Pavilion,

432
00:20:26,160 --> 00:20:27,760
I'm always blinded by anger.

433
00:20:28,380 --> 00:20:29,780
But from Wang Lin's case,

434
00:20:30,370 --> 00:20:33,580
I can see His Majesty's determination
to restore the court.

435
00:20:33,580 --> 00:20:35,030
Given the current situation of Dacang,

436
00:20:35,030 --> 00:20:37,290
all that matters is peace and stability.

437
00:20:37,440 --> 00:20:37,960
Leyu,

438
00:20:38,430 --> 00:20:40,400
what we need to protect is Dacang,

439
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:41,760
isn't it?

440
00:20:47,510 --> 00:20:50,170
Yin Cong, that's exactly
the right way to think.

441
00:20:51,930 --> 00:20:53,060
Where are you going?

442
00:20:54,560 --> 00:20:56,160
I can't keep hiding anymore.

443
00:20:56,400 --> 00:20:58,400
Hiding forever isn't the solution.

444
00:20:58,510 --> 00:21:01,050
Although the corruption case
has been thoroughly investigated,

445
00:21:01,050 --> 00:21:02,370
if I continue to hide,

446
00:21:03,030 --> 00:21:04,110
the wrongful conviction against Lu Yueying

447
00:21:04,110 --> 00:21:05,370
will never be cleared,

448
00:21:05,710 --> 00:21:08,110
and all the despicable schemes behind that

449
00:21:08,190 --> 00:21:09,520
will be buried forever.

450
00:21:10,870 --> 00:21:12,070
So you're going to...

451
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:12,960
That's right.

452
00:21:13,640 --> 00:21:15,240
I believe in today's Dacang.

453
00:21:17,370 --> 00:21:17,900
Let's go.

454
00:21:18,570 --> 00:21:22,230
Petition His Majesty!
Petition His Majesty!

455
00:21:22,230 --> 00:21:26,160
[Petition Drum Hall]

456
00:21:31,400 --> 00:21:33,000
Everyone, please calm down.

457
00:21:34,160 --> 00:21:34,830
Who are you?

458
00:21:35,290 --> 00:21:36,620
Why are you stopping me?

459
00:21:36,930 --> 00:21:38,710
You still need to take the imperial exams
in the future to enter officialdom.

460
00:21:38,710 --> 00:21:41,340
If you beat the drum now,
you'd be opposing the authorities.

461
00:21:41,340 --> 00:21:42,870
Don't ruin your own future.

462
00:21:43,750 --> 00:21:44,830
Ruin my own future?

463
00:21:45,330 --> 00:21:46,060
Our future

464
00:21:46,720 --> 00:21:48,680
