by corrupt officials.

465
00:21:48,680 --> 00:21:49,840
So why should we worry about
ruining it ourselves?

466
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:51,040
-Exactly!
-Exactly!

467
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:52,890
Right, why worry about
ruining it ourselves?

468
00:21:52,890 --> 00:21:54,850
You are... Consort Xian?

469
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:57,430
She's from the Su family.

470
00:21:57,770 --> 00:22:00,370
So you're the eldest daughter
of the Su family.

471
00:22:00,740 --> 00:22:01,800
You noble families

472
00:22:01,960 --> 00:22:03,440
are all cut from the same cloth.

473
00:22:03,440 --> 00:22:05,170
-That's right!
-That's right!

474
00:22:05,950 --> 00:22:07,300
Whether from noble families

475
00:22:07,300 --> 00:22:08,430
or humble families,

476
00:22:09,020 --> 00:22:10,080
everyone is equal.

477
00:22:11,890 --> 00:22:14,150
You want to petition His Majesty, right?

478
00:22:15,680 --> 00:22:16,310
I'll do it.

479
00:22:33,180 --> 00:22:35,660
Great! Great!

480
00:22:39,340 --> 00:22:40,690
Great! Great!

481
00:22:46,880 --> 00:22:48,960
Great! Well struck!

482
00:22:49,050 --> 00:22:51,140
Great! Well struck!

483
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,680
I, Su Leyu, am beating the drum today

484
00:22:58,240 --> 00:23:00,300
not for myself, nor for the Su family.

485
00:23:00,750 --> 00:23:02,950
I wish to seek justice for all scholars,

486
00:23:03,180 --> 00:23:04,700
for Ming Qian,

487
00:23:05,760 --> 00:23:07,430
and for Lu Yueying!

488
00:23:07,980 --> 00:23:14,300
We want justice! We want justice!

489
00:23:14,320 --> 00:23:16,110
Step back! Don't cause trouble!

490
00:23:16,110 --> 00:23:17,260
Hurry, move!

491
00:23:18,190 --> 00:23:19,120
What do you want?

492
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:28,160
The imperial examination fraud

493
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:29,690
disheartens the scholars.

494
00:23:30,100 --> 00:23:32,160
I, Su Leyu, daughter of the Su family,

495
00:23:32,880 --> 00:23:33,850
am beating the petition drum

496
00:23:33,850 --> 00:23:36,420
for all scholars today,

497
00:23:36,570 --> 00:23:39,350
requesting a re-investigation
of the imperial examination fraud case!
